2"><span>link</span></a></li><li class="ctSocialShare_email"><a href="mailto:?to=&subject=CT Pastors: How Are Pastors Handling Ungathered Worship?&body=https://www.christianitytoday.com/pastors/2020/march-web-exclusives/how-are-pastors-handling-un-gathered-worship.html"><span>email</span></a></li><li class="ctSocialShare_print"><a class="ctSocialShare_smallWindow js-openWindow js-trackJanrainClick" href="/pastors/channel/utilities/print.html?type=article&id=181372" title="Print this page" data-eventaction="Print"><span>print</span></a></li></ul>
